Ghana / New Juaben South Municipal / gambiae / 2012 / Q4#

This cohort comprises 23 samples from the gambiae taxon, collected from 1 locations within the administrative division of New Juaben South Municipal, Eastern Region, Ghana. Collections were made in November 2012.
